---
title: Pan-Seared Chicken Tenders and Horseradish Cream with Green Beans and Creamy Mash
description: Golden-brown chicken tenders adorned with green beans and creamy mash are a match made in heaven, while horseradish adds the perfect zip to tonight's pan sauce. It's a fine-dining meal without having to leave the house!
